  "texts": [
    "When viewed across time, it was observed that the use of AI techniques, in terms of the number of unique techniques employed, was growing at an exponential rate (Table 11).",
    "2018 appeared to be the inflexion point.",
    "In 2018, there were a count of seven unique AI techniques applied by the papers in this emerging field.",
    "By 2022, this number grew by more than 18 times, to 129.",
    "The bump graph analysis in Fig. 8 provided a visualization of the evolution."
  ]
}